1)  Don't understand the difference between a right click and left click<br>
2)  Don't understand what the desktop is, until i explain that it's the screen with all the little pictures that you click on to 'get into' programs<br>
<br>
but my biggest pet peeve recently:<br>
3)  Trying to troubleshoot problems that require all users to remain out of the software, only to find out that while I've been on the phone with X person for 30 minutes, person Y has logged back into the software for "just a minute".... therefore screwing up the past 27 minutes of work.  bleck! :)<br>
